            <p class="display-4">About Us</p>
            <p class="lead">Whether you need a web based solution, native smartphone solution or secure coroporate solutions for desktops, Merge Media will be able to help you at a very affordable price point. Contact us to get a quote and find out more.</p>
            <div class="row hidden-md-down">
