                    <p>Desktop applications are great solutions for businesses that want to scale up or create secure, robust solutions for their company. We can develop solutions for you for Mac, Linux and Windows. Contact us to find out more.</p>

                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 mb-3">
